  metaDescription: 'Direct booking engines, PMS integrations, guest experience apps and revenue management tools for Australian hotels, restaurants, tourism operators and venue groups. Technology that fills rooms, tables and experiences.',

  industryName: 'Hospitality & Tourism',
  heroHeadline: 'Hospitality Technology That Fills Rooms and Tables',
  heroTagline: 'Booking platforms, PMS integrations and guest experience tools for hotels, restaurants, tourism operators and venue groups.',

  /* stats array emptied, values were fabricated specific claims ($500M+ TVL, 60% improvements, $2M+ savings, etc.) with no verifiable basis. */

