      description: 'Hotel property management systems, restaurant point-of-sale, spa booking and activities scheduling rarely share data. Front desk staff manually reconcile charges, maintenance requests fall through the gaps and guest spend data lives in silos that make upselling and personalisation nearly impossible.',
    },
    {
      icon: `<svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>`,
